{
  "title": "Lazy-Sunday Roasted Greek Lamb Poach",
  "description": "A delicious and easy-to-make roasted lamb dish from Greece, featuring a rich red wine jelly and a poached egg for a satisfying lazy Sunday meal.",
  "cuisine": "greek",
